          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After each time one of your units fails an Act of Faith roll, for the rest of the battle, add 1 to the D3 roll for this unit’s Mobile Triage ability.</characteristic>
