          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit’s Move step, roll a D3. Then, a number of times equal to the result, select a friendly infantry unit within 6” of this unit, and that unit Heals 1.</characteristic>
